{"tid":2036539,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記為購票者全數回水","createTime":"2020-05-26T13:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T13:55:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e58f9b8e45665cee914becce8da4dfd7b02b62c","tid":2036539,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】繼多支英超球隊之後，榜首利物浦周二宣佈，為不同購票者退回款項。<br />\n<br />\n由於英超復季也是閉門作賽，利物浦官方證實，季票持有者和已購買主場門票的粉絲可獲得退款。紅軍早於上月已表明，購買之後4場主場門票的球迷，皆可獲得退款，及至周二再公佈詳細安排，指購買了紅軍女子隊對愛華頓門票的球迷，一樣會獲得退款。<br />\n<br />\n季票持有者可按比例獲得退還餘下主場比賽的款項，如購買了不同單場比賽的球迷，亦會全數獲得「回水」，而紅軍會在未來14日逐一聯絡購票人，提供更多退款資訊，<br />\n<br />\n紅軍未來兩場主場對水晶宮和阿士東維拉，因已全部售罄，預計單是門票上的損失已高達1200萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"18fbe39303c6d5cf6b8ee879667e2062274a7d09","tid":2036539,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"最重要英超冠軍唔好回水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2499d47bc7642ddcb51be867d912b9a09f1d8a","tid":2036539,"uid":148002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"猁迷最撚on9"},{"pid":"cbf3f52a2bfdade8a432c1524dbed98829bc7df7","tid":2036539,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67e0ea15f7c5f437b4342fb524d32b1aca81c8fc","tid":2036539,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HpFL04AopaQ/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FHpFL04AopaQ%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f7902b23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0a1977caf0a829a780919c8bbe0dbdf16757640","tid":2036539,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:55:40.000Z","msg":"無利迷入場就唔會再重演希素慘劇<br />\n球員放心好多"}]}